{"tid":99909,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有5Mil, 要解決退休 & 住屋, 點搞好???","createTime":"2017-01-29T14:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T05:42:39.000Z","uid":59211,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c2fb723dad3593338f293282038f57a97758e6","tid":99909,"uid":59211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:42:08.000Z","msg":"我就25歲, 做左野一年, 搵15k<br />\n有個呀媽(主婦)<br />\n仲有個細佬, 仲有兩年先大學畢業<br />\n老豆57歲, 月入20k, 三年後退休, 退休金應該有 200萬<br />\n幾年前賣左樓, 有300萬<br />\n依家租緊樓, 每月13k<br />\n<br />\n煩緊點樣可以解決父母退休 &amp; 住屋需要<br />\n1- 租一世樓, 500萬 買 高息股, 以息交租<br />\n我同細佬就癡屋企住, 買樓就靠自己<br />\n<br />\n2- 分兩份做首期, 分別用我名 &amp; 老豆名買<br />\n3- 老豆成日想退休後轉走晒D 錢, 佢同老母就排公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實都好煩惱, 幾時買, 點樣買, 買唔買<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9106c53d77fffa03f6142f4aa4d184426cdaf84","tid":99909,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:53:05.000Z","msg":"反而想知你老豆當年點買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a77d64a8e888684f309dbcf2eee0e7125a7a82","tid":99909,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:59:31.000Z","msg":"買樓日日賺"},{"pid":"6630be601e1f80b8bb9d04647a26a03cccf02345","tid":99909,"uid":47360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"如果係認真 mode<br />\n巴打應該將層樓按來做首期<br />\n等自己同細佬分別上車<br />\n$5m好快用晒"},{"pid":"d3d013095282e8616a7072b2fcd43c5c25060289","tid":99909,"uid":53510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"過大海all in 兩口先"},{"pid":"9a8b0e7c126212d9cd5f489535bb9487bbc59c54","tid":99909,"uid":59211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:53:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而想知你老豆當年點買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />